{"about_the_game":"Hyperglide lets you experience thrilling wingsuit action in beautiful worlds. It features infinite procedural levels, so every time you play, you're presented with a new level to spice things up.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTo collect points, simply fly close to a wall, collect some gems, fly through waterfalls and birds flocks or try to find all five artifacts spread throughout the level. All this will stack in your trick-combo score and who knows, perhaps it will get you a spot in the global leaderboards. The closer and faster you fly to a wall, the more your points will multiply, so risky flying is rewarded but not required because after all, it's most important that you don't crash.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHyperglide supports controller, keyboard or mouse to steer. The controls are very easy to learn and it will only take you a few tries to get the hang of it. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nAdditionally you can switch between third and first person view at any time.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"JUNIOR EXPLORER","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1638520/652cf3f76aa3d704c5f9f6a7564c8a56d0ef4621.jpg"},{"name":"MASTER EXPLORER","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1638520/c0bf74df572c6d1aa34e95486d5ff787830ff38e.jpg"},{"name":"HYPER EXPLORER","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1638520/475512ee8ff6ecb3aa5705eb4c886cd684aaca30.jpg"},{"name":"ADVANCED EXPLORER","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1638520/52fb42beffecf1db0733a9274d0519ab101a68a3.jpg"},{"name":"ULTRA EXPLORER","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1638520/9205687a47213d4376a21bd7c545e4785192935d.jpg"},{"name":"OUCH","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1638520/26500ab0084b24ce79bb42ece9a0e371d5fb09e0.jpg"},{"name":"REPAIR TIME","path":"https://cdn.akamai.ste